name: Get A Through
description:
You play as a Frogo a square like frog. I know strange, but he comes across a species called Spring. The Spring King took all the Fly Money and you have to collect them ALL back. Think you can bring back the money, as well as stop Spring King, and his enemies? Just wait and find out. 

Instruction:

- Use the ARROW KEYS TO MOVE and DOUBLE JUMP

- When you come across the Spring King use the SPACE BAR to ATTACK him.

- You may press the 'R" button to restart levels
